00:25:15.260 --> 00:25:18.820
but amounts to a ego trip -

00:25:19.580 --> 00:25:26.580
[INTERPRETER]

00:25:27.320 --> 00:25:30.560
- is not reality.
- [INTERPRETER]

00:25:32.060 --> 00:25:39.600
