00:25:39.900 --> 00:25:46.960
[INTERPRETER]

00:25:47.460 --> 00:25:52.420
Now in our system there is something called Autonomous Nervous System,

00:25:53.200 --> 00:26:00.020
which means, auto means somebody driven by self.

00:26:00.920 --> 00:26:05.900
It is driven by self - autonomous. So, what is this self?

00:26:06.560 --> 00:26:13.060
[INTERPRETER]

00:26:13.300 --> 00:26:16.460
[INTERPRETER]

00:26:16.700 --> 00:26:23.980
Now, this Autonomous Nervous System is divided into Sympathetic and Parasympathetic Nervous Systems within us.

00:26:24.220 --> 00:26:31.180
[INTERPRETER]

00:26:31.400 --> 00:26:38.780
On the subtler level, the left side that you see here, what we call as Ida Nadi, in the Sanskrit language,

00:26:39.060 --> 00:26:44.220
manifests the left, the Left Sympathetic Nervous System

00:26:44.640 --> 00:26:51.500
and the one which is on the right hand side, which starts from the Swadhishtana - the yellow colored one -

00:26:51.800 --> 00:26:56.760
is the one, what we call as, the Pingala Nadi.

00:26:57.540 --> 00:27:04.180
[INTERPRETER]

00:27:04.360 --> 00:27:09.840
[INTERPRETER]

00:27:10.060 --> 00:27:16.320
[INTERPRETER]

00:27:16.620 --> 00:27:23.380
- It manifests the Right Sympathetic Nervous System.
- [INTERPRETER]

00:27:23.600 --> 00:27:31.660
Now the central path, that you see here half-broken, is the path of Kundalini,

00:27:32.820 --> 00:27:35.820
which, actually, manifests

00:27:36.560 --> 00:27:43.600
in us the Parasympathetic Nervous System and is called as Sushumna Nadi in the Sanskrit language.

00:27:43.940 --> 00:27:49.360
[INTERPRETER]

00:27:49.600 --> 00:27:53.560
[INTERPRETER]

00:27:54.180 --> 00:27:58.160
By the left Nadi, that you see here the blue colored one,

00:27:59.200 --> 00:28:04.460
you desire something - is a power of desire.

00:28:04.740 --> 00:28:09.860
[INTERPRETER]

00:28:10.380 --> 00:28:15.520
- It looks after our emotional side
- [INTERPRETER]

00:28:15.900 --> 00:28:20.980
and is somewhere near Freud's id, we can call it but he was very confused -

00:28:21.380 --> 00:28:27.060
but is the one that looks after your past and your conditioning.

00:28:27.920 --> 00:28:32.480
[INTERPRETER]

00:28:32.800 --> 00:28:37.060
[INTERPRETER]

00:28:37.480 --> 00:28:42.460
So, this is the one that gives you your conditioning or your past.

00:28:42.940 --> 00:28:48.740
[INTERPRETER]

00:28:49.280 --> 00:28:56.540
Now the right side one that you see, the yellow one, is the one that gives you your future

00:28:57.040 --> 00:29:01.000
[INTERPRETER]

00:29:02.680 --> 00:29:08.580
and this is the one which works on your physical and your mental level

00:29:09.200 --> 00:29:14.760
[INTERPRETER]

00:29:15.360 --> 00:29:23.360
so that you have now - left hand side is emotional and the physical and the mental side on the right side.

00:29:24.320 --> 00:29:30.920
[INTERPRETER]

00:29:31.100 --> 00:29:34.680
I must confess, English language is extremely confusing

00:29:35.220 --> 00:29:39.020
[INTERPRETER]

00:29:39.200 --> 00:29:43.160
because the one who suffers from the mental side,

00:29:43.900 --> 00:29:48.640
uh.. they say, is actually suffering from the emotional side

00:29:49.300 --> 00:29:52.580
[INTERPRETER]

00:29:52.840 --> 00:29:58.400
[INTERPRETER]

00:29:58.760 --> 00:30:03.340
So, let us take an exact word for that, is the

00:30:03.540 --> 00:30:07.820
when we say the mind, we mean the emotional side.

00:30:08.420 --> 00:30:12.080
[INTERPRETER]

