00:32:01.980 --> 00:32:05.360
or a dog - he will just go through, he will not have any problems

00:32:05.680 --> 00:32:09.280
but for a human-being, to go through a dirty lane, will be very difficult.

00:32:09.720 --> 00:32:17.540
[INTERPRETER]

00:32:17.740 --> 00:32:22.960
- [INTERPRETER]
- So, on our Central Nervous System

00:32:23.700 --> 00:32:31.040
we have built-in a new capacity to see beauty, to see color, to see uh..

00:32:32.060 --> 00:32:35.880
the dirt and filth, on our Central Nervous System.

00:32:36.300 --> 00:32:41.280
[INTERPRETER]

00:32:41.480 --> 00:32:46.140
[INTERPRETER]

00:32:46.260 --> 00:32:50.740
