00:33:01.980 --> 00:33:08.820
The smell of the musk need not be vowed for; It exists, you can see it yourself.

00:33:09.680 --> 00:33:17.620
[INTERPRETER]

00:33:18.060 --> 00:33:24.740
In the same way, our Central Nervous System records all that we have gained

00:33:25.020 --> 00:33:30.920
through our past, through our conditioning and also what we think about our future.

00:33:31.460 --> 00:33:37.500
[INTERPRETER]

00:33:37.740 --> 00:33:43.720
[INTERPRETER]

